WWW-YouTube-Download version 0.02
=================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  - Carp::Assert
  - URI::Escape

